            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>Welcome to our blog! We are Axel & Jules, a creative couple based in London. Axel is a street photographer capturing the essence of urban life, while Jules is a jewellery designer creating unique pieces inspired by our travels. Our blog documents our life together, exploring how our creative disciplines inspire and intertwine from our hometown in London to our frequented corners of Europe and beyond.</p>
            <p>Through our lens, we bring to light the hidden gems of the world, offering a unique perspective on photography and jewellery design. Join us on our journey as we share insights into the art we create and the places we discover.</p>
